title: Last Christmas

description.plain: “Last Christmas” is a song by Wham! It’s been widely covered by a multitude of artists, including Taylor Swift and Jimmy Eat World. The song reached No. 1 in 2 countries and reached No. 2 in eight countries. It tells the story of a failed relationship and the sadness that the holiday triggers.
